1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Why you feel tired even
after 8 hours of sleep.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
You slept 8 hours. You should feel great.
But you feel like you slept 4.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Sleep hours are only half the equation. Your circadian alignment matters more.
If your light exposure is wrong, 8 hours won't save you.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Bright mornings. Dim evenings.
That's the reset.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
I built an app that fixes
this. 30 seconds to start. Free.

